  "prompt": "What is the definition of dude?",
  "response": "\"Dude\" is an informal term that is commonly used in English-speaking countries. It typically refers to a man or a person, and it can be used in a casual or friendly manner. Originally, it was used in the late 19th century to describe a man who was overly concerned with his appearance or fashion, often from the city visiting the rural American West. Over time, the term evolved to become more generically synonymous with \"guy\" or \"person.\" In contemporary usage, \"dude\" can also be used to refer to someone of any gender, particularly among younger people. It serves as a versatile term in conversation, often conveying familiarity or camaraderie.",
